Requirements
--------------------------

To use this program, yo need to install this python packages:

- python-wxgtk2.8
- python-pyaudio
- python-numpy 
- python-scipy
- python-matplotlib

And this program:

- lilypond

In Debian system, you can write:

	apt-get install python-wxgtk2.8 python-pyaudio python-numpy python-scipy python-matplotlib lilypond

Then, to launch the program, you can do this:

	- Give it execution permissions and then: $ ./music_score_creator.py
	- Execute with: $ python main.py